<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>{% block subject %}Vite & Gourmand{% endblock %}</title>
    <style>
        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
        body {
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f0;
            color: #333333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        .wrapper {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 40px auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            border-radius: 8px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 24px rgba(0,0,0,0.08);
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #2d5016;
            padding: 32px 40px;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .header h1 {
            color: #c9a961;
            font-size: 26px;
            font-weight: 700;
            letter-spacing: 0.04em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .header p {
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.75);
            font-size: 13px;
            margin-top: 4px;
            letter-spacing: 0.08em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }
        .divider {
            height: 4px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #2d5016 0%, #c9a961 50%, #2d5016 100%);
        }
        .content {
            padding: 40px;
        }
        .content h2 {
            color: #2d5016;
            font-size: 20px;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }
        .content p {
            color: #555555;
            font-size: 15px;
            margin-bottom: 14px;
        }
        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 24px 0;
            padding: 14px 32px;
            background-color: #2d5016;
            color: #ffffff !important;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 15px;
            font-weight: 600;
            letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        }
        .highlight-box {
            background-color: #f9f6ee;
            border-left: 4px solid #c9a961;
            padding: 16px 20px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            border-radius: 0 4px 4px 0;
        }
        .highlight-box p {
            margin-bottom: 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background-color: #f5f5f0;
            padding: 24px 40px;
            text-align: center;
            border-top: 1px solid #e8e8e0;
        }
        .footer p {
            color: #888888;
            font-size: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 4px;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #2d5016;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="wrapper">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Vite &amp; Gourmand</h1>
            <p>Restaurant &amp; Traiteur</p>
        </div>
        <div class="divider"></div>
        <div class="content">
            {% block content %}{% endblock %}
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© {{ "now"|date("Y") }} Vite &amp; Gourmand — Tous droits réservés</p>
            <p>Si vous n'êtes pas à l'origine de cette action, ignorez cet email.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
